articles.author: Hilary Whiteman, Angus Watson
articles.title: Clashes in Sydney over Israeli president’s visit as police disperse mass protests - cnn.com
articles.description: Israeli President Isaac Herzog received two very different receptions in Australia on Monday – a warm welcome by a government determined to show solidarity with its grieving Jewish community, and mass protests by activists who consider him a war criminal.
